summaries.short: In the Season Two premiere, Ray's new co-partnership with Tanya and Lenore starts inauspiciously when he holds back during a tryst.
summaries.full: In the Season Two premiere, Ray's new co-partnership with Tanya and Lenore starts inauspiciously when he holds back during a tryst with a pregnant client. Later, Ray and other teachers picket the school in anticipation of summer layoffs. Looking to get an edge on Lenore, Tanya ventures into a tough neighborhood for some liberating pimping advice from a real pro.

summaries.full: (Season One Finale). Alarmed by a bad omen, Tanya ends up battling Lenore for control of Ray. Damon turns to Darby for advice and comfort.

summaries.short: Ray and Jessica face separate identity crises; Tanya seethes at her new boss and at Lenore.
summaries.full: Ray gets more than he bargained for during an impromptu visit with Claire. Later, he tries to prove that he's not an insensitive ex-jock. Seething from the demands of her new boss at work, Tanya turns to Charlie for advice on how to deal with an even more irritable problem: Lenore. Meanwhile, Jessica feels the pinch of the economic downturn, but can't stomach Ronnie's remedy.
